item.title: Lea Salonga & Brad Kane - A Whole New World - Key of D, F - ukeplayalongs
item.description: Play along video for the song A Whole New World by Lea Salonga & Brad Kane from the channel ukeplayalongs. Chords used in the song: A, A7, Bm, B♭, B♭dim7, C, C7, D, Dm, E7, Edim7, Em, E♭, F, F♯7, G, G7, Gm.
